description: Replace career confusion with career confidence, whether you want to improve in your current position, change jobs, or start your own enterprise. This hands-on, experiential course teaches you step-by-step how to define and redesign your Personal Business Model™ — the logic by which you create and deliver value. Gain clarity and power at work by mastering the systematic, repeatable way to optimize the most important business model of all: business model you. Taught directly by the author of the global bestseller Business Model You.
title: Redesign Your Career with a new Personal Business Model
